text: Shantaram Tukaram More is a member of the 13th Maharashtra Legislative Assembly. He represents the Bhiwandi Rural Assembly Constituency. He belongs to the Shiv Sena. ==Positions held== * 2014: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly ==See also== * Bhiwandi Lok Sabha constituency ==References== ==External links== * Shiv Sena Official website Category:Members of the Maharashtra Legislative Assembly Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Living people Category:Shiv Sena politicians Category:People from Thane district Category:Marathi politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
